en_64290_0	A father and his son and Grandmother were killed while another 3 persons were injured after a bus collided with a car at Daladagama Junction in Mahawa, Kurunegala today.
en_64290_1	The mother and another women are currently receiving treatment at the Kurunagala teaching hospital.
en_64290_2	The driver of the bus has been arrested over the incident.
